          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer111919972" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3560398557110969262">A novel of the relationship between Princess Michael and Kind David.<br/>She feels he is keeping her a prisoner and will not allow her to have a life long after he has lost interest in her. Quite sad.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

