              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6945362675326822145">The voice of Michal is clear and strongly written in this story. Women throughout history have had to find various ways to survive in the world, especially when it is an oppressive patriarchal society. The world of David&apos;s time and his story is well imagined with enough details to fill in the gaps but not be overwhelming. There is also a very clear narrative style here that allows for real engagement with the story. An enjoyable read even though the outcome was already known.<br/><br/>&quot;It was a simple sec</span>
  <span id="freeText6945362675326822145" style="display:none">The voice of Michal is clear and strongly written in this story. Women throughout history have had to find various ways to survive in the world, especially when it is an oppressive patriarchal society. The world of David's time and his story is well imagined with enough details to fill in the gaps but not be overwhelming. There is also a very clear narrative style here that allows for real engagement with the story. An enjoyable read even though the outcome was already known.<br /><br />"It was a simple secret, hard learned.<br />To love is to be wise." p.376</span>
